Anybody with an android phone that wants to see if the app will work for walking/biking/driving, the latest version is pushed to master. However, it updates activity every 2 minutes and only will update the stylized image after a visibility change (i.e. locking then unlocking the phone) so it might be hard to see (and maybe dangerous)… don’t test and drive. However, because it checks every two minutes, there should be a small window right when you get to your destination that you can check and see if it worked :simple_smile:
